contentrichtext.text: '''Zábřeh''' is name of several locations in the [[Czech Republic]]: * [[Zábřeh]] (also referred to as '''Zábřeh na Moravě''', {{lang-de|[[Hohenstadt]]}}), a town in [[Olomouc Region]] ([[Šumperk District]]) ** [[Zábřeh Castle]] ** Zábřeh na Moravě, name of the railway station * village Zábřeh is administrative part of town [[Dolní Benešov]] * village [[Zábřeh nad Odrou]] is administrative part of city of [[Ostrava]] == See also == * [[Zabrzeg]] (Polish form) {{geodis}} {{DEFAULTSORT:Zabreh}} [[Category:Czech toponyms]]
